metadata.name: Digital Sketchbook 001
metadata.description:
This is the first in an ongoing series called #digitalsketchbooknft I’ve always kept a sketchbook since high school as drawing as much as possible for yourself is what I find puts me at ease in this World.
I believe that as a commercial artist it’s essential to make personal self directed artwork to stay sane and voice that inner dialog. In the past few years I’ve been creating more and more digitally and building up a portfolio of digital sketches at random just like I do in my traditional ink on paper sketchbooks. Life is fleeting so leave your mark. 
1/1 and more to come ….
